# Sprint 1 — Auth API contract, JWT, and environment

## Repository scan (implementation baseline)

| Area | Current state |
|------|----------------|
| **`middleware.ts`** | Present — pass-through for `/`, `/login`, `/signup`, `/me`, `/logout`; JWT auth remains client-side (localStorage) per Sprint 1. |
| **`next.config.ts`** | Default Next config + **`initOpenNextCloudflareForDev()`** for **`getCloudflareContext()`** in local dev ([OpenNext Cloudflare bindings](https://opennext.js.org/cloudflare/bindings)). |
| **`open-next.config.ts`** | Default **`defineCloudflareConfig({})`** — no custom incremental cache. |
| **`wrangler.jsonc`** | Worker entry **`.open-next/worker.js`**, **`nodejs_compat`**, **`ASSETS`** binding; D1 binding **`quizmaker_app_database`** with **`migrations/`**. |
| **API routes** | **`src/app/api/auth/signup`**, **`login`**, **`logout`**, **`src/app/api/me`** — App Router `route.ts` per Next 15. |

This document is the **single normative contract** for Sprint 1 auth. Paths below **replace** tentative alternatives (`/api/auth/register` vs `/api/auth/signup`, etc.) cited elsewhere.

---

## 1. Style and base paths

| Decision | Value |
|----------|--------|
| **Style** | **REST** over JSON — no tRPC/GraphQL for Sprint 1. |
| **Base** | Same origin as the Next app — browser calls **`/api/...`** with relative URLs. |
| **Handler layout** | **`src/app/api/auth/<segment>/route.ts`** for `/api/auth/*`; **`src/app/api/me/route.ts`** for **`GET /api/me`** (Next App Router). |

### Canonical endpoints (normative)

| Method | Path | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| `POST` | **`/api/auth/signup`** | Create account (email + password + profile fields). |
| `POST` | **`/api/auth/login`** | Issue JWT access token. |
| `GET` | **`/api/me`** | Current user (requires Bearer token). |
| `POST` | **`/api/auth/logout`** | Optional no-op (**204**) for clients expecting a route; **does not** invalidate JWT server-side in Sprint 1. |

> **Note:** **`GET /api/me`** matches **`docs/sprint-1/prd-auth-frontend.mdc`** and **`docs/sprint-1/prd-auth-backend.mdc`**. Do **not** use `/api/auth/me` for Sprint 1 unless this file is amended.

